sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Appliance as Appliance Frontend+Backend
    participant OrgManager as Organization Manager
    participant UserEmail as User Email
    participant Email as Email Service
    participant Worker as Onboarding Worker
    participant DB as Database
    participant NuNet as NuNet CLI
    participant OpenBao as OpenBao PKI
    participant Elastic as Elasticsearch

    User->>Appliance: Select organization
    Appliance->>Appliance: Load known organizations
    Appliance->>Appliance: Update state: collect_join_data
    
    User->>Appliance: Fill and submit form
    Appliance->>Appliance: Validate form
    Appliance->>Appliance: Capture DMS resources
    Appliance->>OrgManager: POST /onboarding/submit/
    OrgManager->>DB: Create OnboardingRequest
    OrgManager->>DB: Store hardware resources
    OrgManager->>DB: Enrich with GeoIP data
    OrgManager->>Email: Send verification email
    Email-->>UserEmail: Email sent
    Email-->>OrgManager: Email sent
    OrgManager->>DB: Update status: email_sent
    OrgManager-->>Appliance: {id, status_token, status: "email_sent"}
    Appliance->>Appliance: Update state: join_data_sent
    
    Note over Appliance: Appliance polls for status
    Appliance->>OrgManager: GET /status/id/ with status_token
    OrgManager->>DB: Retrieve request
    OrgManager-->>Appliance: id, status_token, status email_sent
    
    Note over UserEmail: User clicks verification link
    UserEmail->>OrgManager: GET /verify-email/id/token/
    OrgManager->>DB: Validate token
    OrgManager->>DB: Update status: email_verified
    OrgManager-->>UserEmail: Email verified
    
    Note over Appliance: Appliance polls for status
    Appliance->>OrgManager: GET /status/id/ with status_token
    OrgManager->>DB: Retrieve request
    OrgManager-->>Appliance: id, status_token, status email_verified
    
    loop Worker polling loop
        Worker->>OrgManager: POST /worker/heartbeat/
        OrgManager->>DB: Update worker heartbeat
        Worker->>OrgManager: GET /worker/available-requests/
        OrgManager->>DB: Check round-robin this worker turn
        alt Worker's turn
            OrgManager-->>Worker: request available
            Worker->>OrgManager: PUT /worker/claim-request/id/
            OrgManager->>DB: Set claimed_by, status: processing
            
            Worker->>NuNet: nunet cap delegate
            NuNet-->>Worker: Capability token
            
            Worker->>OpenBao: Issue client certificate
            OpenBao-->>Worker: client.crt, client.key, CA bundle
            
            Worker->>Elastic: Create API key
            Elastic-->>Worker: API key
            
            Worker->>OrgManager: PUT /worker/complete-request/id/
            OrgManager->>DB: Store results, status: ready
        else Not worker's turn
            OrgManager-->>Worker: no request
        end
    end
    
    loop Appliance polling loop
        Appliance->>OrgManager: GET /status/id/ with status_token
        OrgManager->>DB: Retrieve request
        OrgManager-->>Appliance: status capability_token and other data
        alt Status: ready
            Appliance->>Appliance: Process payload
            Note over Appliance: Apply tokens, certs, config
            Appliance->>NuNet: nunet cap grant (require token)
            Appliance->>NuNet: nunet cap anchor (provide token)
            Appliance->>Appliance: Configure observability
            Appliance->>Appliance: Write mTLS certificates
            Appliance->>Appliance: Copy tokens to DMS user
            Appliance->>Appliance: Onboard compute
            Appliance->>Appliance: Update state: complete
        end
    end
    
    User->>Appliance: Restart DMS
    Appliance->>Appliance: systemctl restart nunetdms
